data.name: tbInterviewGeneric.Text
data.value: - Find their application (or ask them to make one if they haven't already. - Change the thread prefix to "Accepted" and post the accepted post. - Create their feedback thread using the appropriate content. - Change the application's prefix to "On Trial". - Comment on the application to let them know when their trial starts and ends. - Add the feedback thread link to their description on Teamspeak. - On their application, scroll to the bottom and press "Approve". This will automatically make them a trialist. - Assign them the Trialist rank on Teamspeak.
